  "translations": {
    "en": "O! Hisham indeed al'aql not narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh and not asks who/whoever fears mn'h and not promises what/not not he is able upon him and not hopes what/not is reproached brja'h and not advances upon what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "ur": "اے Hisham بے شک al'aql نہیں narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh اور نہیں asks who/whoever fears mn'h اور نہیں promises what/not نہیں he is able upon him اور نہیں hopes what/not is reproached brja'h اور نہیں advances پر what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "tr": "ey Hisham muhakkak al'aql değil narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh ve değil asks who/whoever fears mn'h ve değil promises what/not değil he is able upon him ve değil hopes what/not is reproached brja'h ve değil advances üzerine what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "fa": "ای Hisham به درستی al'aql نه narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh و نه asks who/whoever fears mn'h و نه promises what/not نه he is able upon him و نه hopes what/not is reproached brja'h و نه advances بر what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "id": "wahai Hisham sesungguhnya al'aql tidak narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh dan tidak asks who/whoever fears mn'h dan tidak promises what/not tidak he is able upon him dan tidak hopes what/not is reproached brja'h dan tidak advances atas what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "bn": "হে Hisham নিশ্চয়ই al'aql না narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh এবং না asks who/whoever fears mn'h এবং না promises what/not না he is able upon him এবং না hopes what/not is reproached brja'h এবং না advances উপর what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "es": "oh Hisham ciertamente al'aql no narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh y no asks who/whoever fears mn'h y no promises what/not no he is able upon him y no hopes what/not is reproached brja'h y no advances sobre what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "fr": "ô Hisham certes al'aql non narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh et non asks who/whoever fears mn'h et non promises what/not non he is able upon him et non hopes what/not is reproached brja'h et non advances sur what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "de": "o Hisham wahrlich al'aql nicht narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh und nicht asks who/whoever fears mn'h und nicht promises what/not nicht he is able upon him und nicht hopes what/not is reproached brja'h und nicht advances auf what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "ru": "о Hisham поистине al'aql не narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh и не asks who/whoever fears mn'h и не promises what/not не he is able upon him и не hopes what/not is reproached brja'h и не advances на what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him .",
    "zh": "啊 Hisham 确实 al'aql 不 narrates who/whoever fears tkdhybh 和 不 asks who/whoever fears mn'h 和 不 promises what/not 不 he is able upon him 和 不 hopes what/not is reproached brja'h 和 不 advances 在...上 what/not fears fwth bal'jz from him ."
